<br />\n仲要成日OT ，人工又唔高<br />\n有時仲會擔心到失眠、無胃口食飯<br />\n<br />\n但份工既滿足感都幾大<br />\n如果連呢個都無埋應該好份辭職"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"巴打你都幾好啊 起碼返工揾到意義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"但返到人無哂精神，身體都差左好多"},{"pid":"b671a5010ab2eab9fad94f498668a678d84c10c3","tid":1023820,"uid":225321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba02e91e1d24bd159ec13fa7d79a67b9d72bd06a","tid":1023820,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"樓主啲口吻咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a97492c528e9bd4b807704fee11e27ea9829d7d","tid":1023820,"uid":225321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3002dd99c1b9e7a84ceffed8f10ba557fc92ee1","tid":1023820,"uid":100017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797ac0c7b839b373c12e7bcb900786a7f6e0700b","tid":1023820,"uid":225321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed65b4e7c8e6a16bf6e9abd8919b787d35fa91a6","tid":1023820,"uid":100017,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"我依家份工返左十個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩返工個兩個月瘦左4Kg<br />\n依家加加埋埋瘦左6Kg<br />\n仲要成日OT ，人工又唔高<br />\n有時仲會擔心到失眠、無胃口食飯<br />\n<br />\n但份工既滿足感都幾大<br />\n如果連呢個都無埋應該好份辭職"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"巴打你都幾好啊 起碼返工揾到意義"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"但返到人無哂精神，身體都差左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"Me too <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0602c3fe55d7fa2b4dfb0023920c1e718fae5b5a","tid":1023820,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43c820c607d22856b18933c32337c8faaf339943","tid":1023820,"uid":85707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T0